{"abstract": "A former president of CBS News, he helped steer the network through a $120 million libel suit by Gen. William C. Westmoreland.", "web_url": "https://www.nytimes.com/2014/08/06/business/edward-m-joyce-cbs-news-leader-during-era-of-cost-cutting-dies-at-81.html", "snippet": "A former president of CBS News, he helped steer the network through a $120 million libel suit by Gen. William C. Westmoreland.", "lead_paragraph": "Edward M. Joyce, a former president of CBS News who in the mid-1980s helped steer the so-called \u201cTiffany network\u201d through a $120 million libel suit by Gen. William C. Westmoreland, deep staff reductions and several takeover threats, died on Saturday at his home in Redding, Conn. He was 81.", "print_section": "B", "print_page": "15", "source": "The New York Times", "multimedia": [{"rank": 0, "subtype": "xlarge", "caption": null, "credit": null, "type": "image", "url": "images/2014/08/06/business/JOYCE-obit/JOYCE-obit-articleLarge.jpg", "height": 607, "width": 600, "subType": "xlarge", "crop_name": "articleLarge", "legacy": {"xlarge": "images/2014/08/06/business/JOYCE-obit/JOYCE-obit-articleLarge.jpg", "xlargewidth": 600, "xlargeheight": 607}}, {"rank": 0, "subtype": "jumbo", "caption": null, "credit": null, "type": "image", "url": "images/2014/08/06/business/JOYCE-obit/JOYCE-obit-jumbo.jpg", "height": 1024, "width": 1013, "subType": "jumbo", "crop_name": "jumbo", "legacy": {}}, {"rank": 0, "subtype": "superJumbo", "caption": null, "credit": null, "type": "image", "url": "images/2014/08/06/business/JOYCE-obit/JOYCE-obit-superJumbo.jpg", "height": 1777, "width": 1757, "subType": "superJumbo", "crop_name": "superJumbo", "legacy": {}}, {"rank": 0, "subtype": "thumbnail", "caption": null, "credit": null, "type": "image", "url": "images/2014/08/06/business/JOYCE-obit/JOYCE-obit-thumbStandard.jpg", "height": 75, "width": 75, "subType": "thumbnail", "crop_name": "thumbStandard", "legacy": {"thumbnail": "images/2014/08/06/business/JOYCE-ob